      Data: 20|UnityEngine.TooltipAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: DEBUG/validation only. After a generator finishes a column, keep its
        slot 'busy' for this many extra frames to SIMULATE Quest's GPU-readback occupancy
        inside ClientSim (where readback is near-instant). Use it to verify on desktop
        that the look-ahead dispatch actually keeps all generators busy concurrently.
        0 = off (no effect on real runs). Leave at 0 for shipping.
